questionsAndAnswers.question: How to make sure you won't disclose private information about my project?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We keep all the information confidential and do not share them among our clients, We also ready to sign NDA for that anywhere if needed.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide all the source code once development is finished ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, We host all the source code on the github and once all the payment are clear we do hand over all the resources to our clients.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How can i use my custom use cases with AI ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We do also train the open source models in order to satisfy our custom needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What are the cloud platform do you work with?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We do work with AWS, Azure, GCP and Digital ocean, We are ready to explore more platform if needed.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can i host my custom model on the server?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes Indeed, You can host your trained model on various service providers like replicate or even you can host it on your own infrastructure.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do you charge ? Is it project based or milestone based ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We do divide the entire project into multiple milestones as deliverables and you can always approve the milestone once you are satisfied with the end results.
